data.description:
This cozy modern farmhouse sits pretty on over a quarter acre of good ol' country soil. This gem is callin' out to first-time homesteaders, a young couple startin' their journey, or folks lookin' for a peaceful spot to enjoy that laid-back empty-nesting life. Tucked close to lakes, camping grounds, and just a jaunt away from a little casino action, this place ain't just a home – it's a ticket to country livin'.

Step on in, where the open living concept is dressed up in warm luxury vinyl flooring, giving the whole place a touch of that rustic charm. Freshly spruced up in 2020, you'll find custom cabinetry, a new roof, and updated windows. The primary bedroom is a genuine retreat with its en-suite bathroom boastin' a walk-in shower.  

This farmhouse is invitin' you to come savor the simple joys of country life. So, what's keepin' you? Swing by and let this farmhouse wrap you in its warm country embrace today – it's ready to be the heart of your country story!
